  <section id="healthcare" class="scroll-mt-24 mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Healthcare in Indonesia</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Indonesia's healthcare is developing but limited compared to Western countries or Singapore. Private facilities in Bali can handle routine care; serious issues often require evacuation.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Healthcare Tiers</h3>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
