        <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Bali Private Hospitals</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
          <li>• BIMC Hospital (Kuta, Nusa Dua) - Best in Bali</li>
          <li>• Siloam Hospital - Modern, good specialists</li>
          <li>• Kasih Ibu Hospital - Affordable option</li>
          <li>• English-speaking staff available</li>
          <li>• Good for routine and moderate care</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Singapore Evacuation</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
          <li>• 2-hour flight from Bali</li>
          <li>• World-class hospitals (Mount Elizabeth, etc.)</li>
          <li>• Complex surgeries, cancer treatment</li>
          <li>• Air ambulance: $15,000-50,000+</li>
          <li>• Standard for serious emergencies</li>
        </ul>
